abstract = {A decline in total PCB levels in tissues of otters (Lutra lutra) from England and Wales, averaging 8% per year over the period 1983-1992, is reported. Mean PCB levels are now unlikely to pose a threat to otter populations. (C) 1998 Elsevier Science Ltd.},
